        <field name="description" type="html">
<p>Our integration works fine most of the time, but roughly 1 in 20 requests fails with a 403 for no obvious reason. We've checked our API key and scopes -- nothing looks wrong on our end.</p>
        </field>
        <field name="ai_triage_done">True</field>
        <field name="ai_triage_accepted">True</field>
